OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778410973
OL,3,CTwo men charged with filming
OL,4,Cantisemitic TikTok videos
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged with
OL,7,Freligiously aggravated harassment over
OL,8,Fallegations they travelled to an area
OL,9,Fwith a significant Jewish population
OL,10,Fto film antisemitic social media
OL,11,Fvideos.
OL,13,FThe Metropolitan Police were called to
OL,14,Freports of a group of men allegedly
OL,15,Fharassing members of the Jewish
OL,16,Fcommunity on Clapton Common in Hackney
OL,17,Fon Thursday night.
OL,19,FThe force said officers arrested five
OL,20,Fmen following the incident.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
