FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778410973
OL,3,CTwo men charged with filming
OL,4,Cantisemitic TikTok videos
OL,6,FThe CPS said Adam Bedouia and
OL,7,FAbdelkader Amir Bousloub were due to
OL,8,Fappear at Thames Magistrates' Court on
OL,9,FSaturday over allegations they
OL,10,Fapproached, harassed and filmed Jewish
OL,11,Fpeople in north London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778410973
OL,3,CTwo men charged with filming
OL,4,Cantisemitic TikTok videos
OL,6,FHuw Rogers, chief crown prosecutor for
OL,7,FCPS Direct, said: "The Crown
OL,8,FProsecution Service has decided to
OL,9,Fcharge Adam Bedoui, 20, and Abdelkader
OL,10,FAmir Bousloub, 21, with religiously
OL,11,Faggravated intentional harassment and
OL,12,Fintentional harassment following an
OL,13,Fincident where Jewish people in
OL,14,FStamford Hill were being approached,
OL,15,Fharassed and filmed.
OL,26,@oD@SOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778410973
OL,3,CTwo men charged with filming
OL,4,Cantisemitic TikTok videos
OL,6,F"Our team of out-of-hours prosecutors
OL,7,Ffrom CPS Direct worked to establish
OL,8,Fthat there is sufficient evidence to
OL,9,Fbring charges and it is in the public
OL,10,Finterest to pursue criminal
OL,11,Fproceedings.
OL,13,F"We have worked closely with the
OL,14,FMetropolitan Police as it has carried
OL,15,Fout its investigation.
OL,17,F"Both defendants are due to appear at
OL,18,FThames Magistrates' Court on Saturday
OL,19,FMay 9 2026."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
