OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778410973
OL,3,CTwo men charged with filming
OL,4,Cantisemitic TikTok videos
OL,6,FThe police said the men, who are both
OL,7,Ffrom Hillingdon, have been released on
OL,8,Fbail pending further enquiries.
OL,10,FDetective Superintendent Oliver
OL,11,FRichter, who leads policing in Hackney
OL,12,Fand Tower Hamlets, said: "Our
OL,13,Finvestigation continues but two men
OL,14,Fhave been charged and will appear in
OL,15,Fcourt for their alleged part in this
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,F"We will not tolerate any form of hate
OL,19,Fcrime against our communities."
OL,26,@tD@ZOUzD@AOU{D@_O]
